  "title": "Dental Assistant at Punggol",
  "description": "<p>We are an established boutique Dental Clinic in Punggol Plaza.</p><p>If you're passionate about patient care and have a strong work ethic, we would like to invite you to join our family as a Dental Assistant. </p><p><strong>Job description:</strong></p><p>- Provide chair-side assistance to dentists</p><p>- Assist in the taking of dental X-ray and ensure patient safety and comfort</p><p>- Help to ensure cleanliness and sterility of dental instruments and equipment</p><p>- Comply with infection control practices and maintains Infection control standards</p><p>- Maintain cleanliness and tidiness of the treatment room / work station</p><p>- Educate patients on oral and post-treatment care</p><p>- Help with reception duties and inventory management</p><p><strong>We're looking for:</strong></p><p>- Min GCE 'N' level or equivalent<br /><br />- Experience in dental assisting preferred</p><p>- Singaporean / PR only</p><p>- Team player with good communication and interpersonal skills and positive attitude</p><p><strong>Working arrangements:</strong></p><p>- 5 days work-week inclusive of Saturdays and late afternoon shifts</p><p>- Work at one location only</p><p><strong>Staff benefits:</strong></p><p>- Annual leave</p><p>- Performance bonus</p><p>- Competitive salary (Negotiable)</p><p><br /></p><p>WhatsApp your resume to us at <strong>80618998 </strong>today!</p>",
